{
  "texts": [
    "UAVs or drones have impacted several sectors and have become almost indispensable in daily operations in the commercial world.",
    "They are employed in capturing images from the sky and acquiring information that will be relayed to base stations to aid in decision making, especially in areas of surveillance and monitoring (Rogers, 2018).",
    "The overall advancement in the use and application of drones, especially in day-to-day activities, has, however, come with several impacts.",
    "This has raised concerns over the safety and security of the public, hence calling for definite legislation over the matter establishing accountability for the privacy of individuals and the public at large (Robakowska et al., 2019).",
    "Despite the present challenges, small-sized drones are increasingly being adopted in various industries, such as agriculture, shipping, and manufacturing industries, among others."
  ]
}